## When to use which

- Round-trip a citation: PubMed E-utilities. Always.
- Find papers citing a known landmark: Semantic Scholar.
- Look for systematic reviews on a treatment question: Cochrane first, then PubMed with `[Publication Type]` filter for systematic-review.
- Check whether a candidate is in trials: ClinicalTrials.gov.
- Background on standard-of-care: society guidelines + consensus statements (filled during frontier scan).
